flavor_text_entries.red:
A strange seed was
planted on its
back at birth. The plant sprouts
and grows with
this POKéMON.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
A strange seed was
planted on its
back at birth. The plant sprouts
and grows with
this POKéMON.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
It can go for days
without eating a
single morsel. In the bulb on
its back, it
stores energy.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
The seed on its
back is filled
with nutrients. The seed grows
steadily larger as
its body grows.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It carries a seed
on its back right
from birth. As it grows older, the
seed also grows
larger.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
While it is young,
it uses the
nutrients that are stored in the
seeds on its back
in order to grow.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
BULBASAUR can be seen napping in
bright sunlight.
There is a seed on its back. By soaking up the sun’s rays, the seed
grows progressively larger.
